## Quick Reference Command Dashboard

```bash
# --- HOST DISCOVERY & PATHS ---
ping -c 5 10.145.191.225               # Ping (Linux)
ping -n 5 10.145.191.225               # Ping (Windows)
traceroute 10.145.191.225              # Trace Path (Linux UDP)
traceroute -T 10.145.191.225           # Trace Path (Linux TCP - Bypass Filters)
tracert 10.145.191.225                 # Trace Path (Windows)
mtr 10.145.191.225                     # Live Path Monitoring

# --- BANNER GRABBING & PORT PROBING ---
nc 10.145.191.225 80                   # Netcat TCP Connection
nc -vnlp 1234                          # Netcat Listen on Port 1234
curl -I http://10.145.191.225          # Fetch Web Server Headers
openssl s_client -connect 10.145.191.225:443 # Grab SSL/TLS Service Banner

```
